                # 1. Get me the IP address of a particular domain (guvi.in)
dig guvi.in

               # 2. How do I find the CPU/memory usage of my server?
top

               # 3. Test the connectivity between 2 nodes.
           # i use ping command following by ip address that you wanted to check connectivity with. for ex. i use IP address of guvi.in
ping 172.67.70.207
